## RelationType: 采购订单关联物料

采购订单与物料之间的关联关系。物料采购订单PO是关于某个物料的采购，基于物料编码来进行连接

### Endpoint

| Source | Target | Type |
|--------|--------|------|
| po | material | direct |

### Mapping Rules

| Source Property | Target Property |
|-----------------|-----------------|
| material_number | material_code |
